OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBecoming cloudy and mild with
OL,6,Fsome brighter spells, later spells of
OL,7,Frain will spread eastwards across the
OL,8,Fregion by the evening. Moderate winds
OL,9,Fgusty at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloudy with rain, mainly in
OL,12,Fthe west and over high ground with
OL,13,Fhill fog. Elsewhere dry and mild.
OL,14,FBreezy along the coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FCloudy and mild with
OL,17,Foccasional rain on Thursday, mainly in
OL,18,Fthe west with strengthening winds.
OL,19,FRain easing overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
